v = ['#2A788EEE', '#2A788E66',
     '#440154EE', '#44015466',
     '#7AD151EE', '#7AD15166']

def heatmapHelper(a, b, o):
    sns.set()
    fig = plt.figure(figsize = (10, 10))
    ax = fig.add_subplot(xlim = (0, 10),
                         ylim = (0, 10))

    #Title setup.
    ax.set_title("Hacking Gymnastics Scores", fontsize = 24)

    #X-axis setup.
    ax.set_xlabel("Gymnast A's Execution Score", fontsize = 20)

    #Y-axis setup.
    ax.set_ylabel("Gymnast B's Execution Score", fontsize = 20)
    
    #Limits
    center = (b, a)
    
    a_min = b * 10 /a
    a_max = b + 10 - a

    b_max = a - b
    
    ax.add_patch(mpP([(0, 0), center, (a_max, 10), (10, 10), (10, 0), (0,0)], label = "A Always Wins", fc = v[2]))
    ax.add_patch(mpP([(0, b_max), (0, 10), (a_min, 10), center, (0, b_max)], label = "B Always Wins", fc = v[0]))
    ax.add_patch(mpP([center, (a_min, 10), (a_max, 10), center], label = "A Wins Multiplication", fc = v[3]))
    ax.add_patch(mpP([(0, 0), (0, b_max), center, (0,0)], label = "B Wins Multiplication", fc = v[1]))
    
    if o == 'ec' :
        ax.axvline(x = b, c = 'k', ls = ':')
        ax.set_xticks(ticks = [])
        ax.axhline(y = a, c = 'k', ls = ':')
        ax.set_yticks(ticks = [])
        
        text = [("(0, a-b)", (0.1, a-b), 'left', 'center', 0),
                ("(b, 0)", (b, 0.1), 'left', 'bottom', 0),
                ("(b, a)", (b-0.1, a+0.1), 'right', 'bottom', 0),
                ("(10b/a, 10)", (10*b/a, 9.9), 'right', 'top', 0),
                ("(b+10-a, 10)", (b+10-a, 9.9), 'left', 'top', 0)]
        
        
        
        for t in text :
            plt.annotate(text = t[0],
                         xy = t[1],
                         c = 'k',
                         size = 16,
                         ha = t[2],
                         va = t[3],
                         zorder = 2)
        ypad = -0.1
        
    else :
        
        ax.set_xticks(ticks = range(11))
        ax.xaxis.set_major_formatter(SMF("{x:.1f}"))
        ax.set_yticks(ticks = range(11))
        ax.yaxis.set_major_formatter(SMF("{x:.1f}"))
        ax.tick_params(axis = 'both', which = 'major', labelsize = 16)
        ypad = -0.15    
    
    ax.legend(loc = 'lower center', bbox_to_anchor = (0.5, ypad), ncol = 4, fancybox = True, shadow = True, fontsize = 14)
    fig.savefig("2024.08.09" + o + ".png", bbox_inches = 'tight')

all = []
for i in range(1, 10001) :
    b = i/1000
    for j in range(i, 10001) :
        a = j/1000
        t1 = ((b+10-a) - b*10/a)*(10-a)/2
        t2 = (a-b)*b / 2
        all.append(t1+t2)
